node.text: (link in bio) We talk about her passion for being in tune with nature. She shares how she encourages open communication with her children, appreciating nature as it is while learning to appreciate our own value, and the healing benefits of incorporating meditation in your daily routine.

node.text:
Saying Yes takes determination ⁠⁠
Saying No takes courage ⁠⁠
Competing requires focus ⁠⁠
Exiting requires bravery ⁠⁠
Achievements are wonderful ⁠⁠
Acceptance is crucial ⁠⁠
Simone has shown us the power of all of these throughout her life. Thank you for allowing us to value each and every one of these choices as important. Putting yourself first before opinions, expectations and obligations takes strength. Let’s honor @simonebiles decision amidst the noise so we can learn to hear our own inner voice more clearly.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Jay Shetty on July 29, 2021. May be an image of one or more people and text that says 'When you work hard for a higher purpose you become more soft hearted. You realize how difficult it is to heal and grow so you're more compassionate to those struggling Working harder doesn't make you more hard hearted it makes you more soft hearted Jay Shetty'.

Leave a ❤️ below for this👇 It's these spur of the moment type experiences where you just decide to go play a game outside with a loved one that are sometimes the most special and most memorable⁠⁠

@jayshettygenius is what happens when weekly coaching, dedicated meditation, and vibrant community all come together. This is the space where I share my private workshops and guided meditations for mind, body, and soul. ⁠⁠
⁠⁠
It's all about coaching 🙌 consistency 💫 and community ❤️ ⁠⁠
⁠⁠

node.text: (link in bio) We talk about her passion for being in tune with nature. She shares how she encourages open communication with her children, appreciating nature as it is while learning to appreciate our own value, and the healing benefits of incorporating meditation in your daily routine.
